{"tid":111751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"邊到學以色列自衛術好啲","createTime":"2017-02-07T15:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T17:11:13.000Z","uid":22361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"725bf7518c55598b0f8f53c3785d1774d345f12a","tid":111751,"uid":22361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"求介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以色列近身格鬥術，又稱以色列搏擊防身術、以色列防衛術（希伯來語：קרב מגע&lrm;英語發音：/krɑːv məˈɡɑː/，Krav Maga，音譯為克拉夫瑪迦、馬伽術，意為近身格鬥）是一種近身格鬥技術、防身術或者運動，而非傳統所謂的武術；以色列搏擊防身術為一種學習對應徒手、刀械、棍棒及槍枝等攻擊，及因應各種不同危險環境而應變的防身體系。"},{"pid":"4e70eea01a5ceba4fc2e8c2e42bf00a97eb2df13","tid":111751,"uid":22361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56fc940dd1a7cc86f0e35be285b144df941f03e2","tid":111751,"uid":22361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45601b4091044b389a05118cd8aedf740ebad4c3","tid":111751,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:46:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2d4ccc9fbe97f49c9051e8dceaf9802670fec322","tid":111751,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:48:08.000Z","msg":"phsh"},{"pid":"e5c48c8d3fb403def8a95ea61ee119292b4bdcf0","tid":111751,"uid":79711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"我都想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bc51bdd613b7bbcfcb6